{"tid":1524552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日大家好嬲，但唔好唔記得入機場既目標","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T02:08:41.000Z","uid":41355,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ce42533ade2291d2f49a8e86e5da51d940bd244d","tid":1524552,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:31:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>目標</ins></strong><br />\n聽日全世界都會聚焦香港<br />\n今晚我同大家一樣都好嬲<br />\n但大家要記住，黑警只係問題既一部分<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">更大既問題係成個政制，同香港遲遲未有雙普選</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日去機場係<del><span style=\"font-size: small;\">表達對政府同中共既不滿</span></del>去觀光<br />\n觀光時記得準備定多d文宣，盡量用英文向世界發聲<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n除左Fight for Freedom, Stand with Hong Kong之外<br />\n可以將香港同世界連接，比如：<br />\nThey don't give us freedom. We give them revolution!<br />\nStand for Hong Kong. Stand for freedom and human dignity<br />\nSupport Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act（香港人權與民主法案）<br />\nFree World VS Chinazi<br />\nFree World VS Totalitarianism<br />\nWE ARE AGAINST THE POLICE STATE. ONLY A COWARD CAN HURT A CHILD.<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>準備</ins></strong><br />\n入機場前帶定食水同少量乾糧，去定toilet<br />\n大家都係遊客，可以出街look<br />\n不過天氣咁熱，<strong>最好帶多套衫換</strong><br />\n諗定邊條路線：車、單車、地鐵、巴士<br />\n搭機鐵既話買張單程車票去最近既車站就夠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>入9月1機場 tg group</strong></ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70mZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=6cbfbd00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a>"},{"pid":"44a528d5a2104aa4924af4bfe7ba423767f727dc","tid":1524552,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:31:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29068978b5eb0b9bc158d2d95805258b1590edeb","tid":1524552,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:32:44.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"e