y<br />\nSupport Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act（香港人權與民主法案）<br />\nFree World VS Chinazi<br />\nFree World VS Totalitarianism<br />\nWE ARE AGAINST THE POLICE STATE. ONLY A COWARD CAN HURT A CHILD.<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>準備</ins></strong><br />\n入機場前帶定食水同少量乾糧，去定toilet<br />\n大家都係遊客，可以出街look<br />\n不過天氣咁熱，<strong>最好帶多套衫換</strong><br />\n諗定邊條路線：車、單車、地鐵、巴士<br />\n搭機鐵既話買張單程車票去最近既車站就夠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>入9月1機場 tg group</strong></ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70mZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=6cbfbd00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:40:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日901 1點鐘 機場見 !!!</span> </strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入機場! 入機場! 入機場!</span><br />\n揸L爆佢春袋!!<br />\n<br />\n高舉海外文宣!! 要大大力推上國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等英美就&lt;&lt;中英聯合聲明&gt;&gt;同&lt;&lt;人權及民主法案&gt;&gt;有牌揸手<br />\n要多人舉先有用!!畫面先夠力!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到呢堆圖嘅巴絲!我哋每人<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">print 10張</span></strong></span>帶入機場! 派埋比隔離左右一齊高舉!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2hJ6TR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2hJ6TR.png&h=1cbd7c2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JiqjFdR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJiqjFdR.png&h=ba7711c9&